Author: John Hiesey (jhiesey@stanford.edu)

To build:
cabal configure
cabal build
(executable is dist/build/wordhist/wordhist)

--OR--

ghc --make WordHist.hs
(executable is WordHist)

To run:
wordhist
    Reads from stdin, use ^D (EOF) to terminate
wordhist file [file...]
    Reads from the given files